{"word":"G1534 - εἶτα - eîta - i'-tah - After that","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἶτα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eîta</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">i'-tah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">After that</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பின்பு, மேலும், அன்றியும் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"then; next; after that"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Of uncertain affinity; a particle of <i>succession</i> (in time or logical enumeration), <i>then</i>, <i>moreover</i>: - after that (-ward), furthermore, then. See also <a href=\"#/G1899 - ἔπειτα - épeita - ep'-i-tah/1899\">G1899</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}